<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/560334-i-have-just-got-this-from-the-library-but">I have just got this from the library but the blurb on the back says &quot;Part of the trilogy that includes The House of the Spirits and Portrait in Sepia&quot;. Do I need to read The House of the Spirits first?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_560334'><a id="like_count_community_question_560334" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/560334?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">5 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F16527.Daughter_of_Fortune">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/560334-i-have-just-got-this-from-the-library-but">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/560334-i-have-just-got-this-from-the-library-but">See all 6 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/47766175-sonia"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/47766175-sonia">Sonia</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;ve read House of the Spirits and watched the movie as well (with Antonio Banderas, Winona Ryder) and there&apos;s nothing to do with Daughter of Fortune.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I've read House of the Spirits and watched the movie as well (with Antonio Banderas, Winona Ryder) and there's nothing to do with Daughter of Fortune. They are not part of the same story. Portrait in Sepia is indeed a sequel, which follows the story of Eliza Sommer's granddaughter. It's not even directly connected to Daughter of Fortune, so you don't need to read it first. <br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

<div class='flagAnswer'>
<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link310645" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=310645&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F560334-i-have-just-got-this-from-the-library-but%2Fanswers%2F310645-i-ve-read-house-of-the">flag</a>
</div>
<ul class='communityQAFooter answerFooter'>
</ul>

</div>
